{"tid":1855624,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[唔封關的原因？] 全世界封強國，唔封香港。假證件可以經香港走佬？","createTime":"2020-02-01T07:42:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T12:37:25.000Z","uid":62935,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6dd94b1be61425e9f870d7e6478774967e00b72e","tid":1855624,"uid":62935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T07:42:47.000Z","msg":"讓XX先走？<br />\n<br />\n只要造到假證扮係香港人，就係最後逃生門逃去歐美......<br />\n<br />\n如果疫情再嚴重...呢個就係國內權貴最後逃生門......"},{"pid":"71fbddad9c0c15f6a4b4d11bef47b21fbc639572","tid":1855624,"uid":184370,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T07:43:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />洗乜做假，你都識講高官"},{"pid":"3424a717cf348bac6bcb0a595acee2e68e21a31d","tid":1855624,"uid":62935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71fbddad9c0c15f6a4b4d11bef47b21fbc639572","tid":1855624,"uid":184370,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T07:43:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />洗乜做假，你都識講高官"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T07:44:56.000Z","msg":"權貴......親屬......"},{"pid":"56be24fd79f9c8169029948310f6000f59b06f29","tid":1855624,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T07:47:27.000Z","msg":"香港再唔封關，好快就比人封我地關<br />\n而林鄭係有心唔封關，目的就係想引入病毒殺香港人，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">你唔係覺得政府會care你無醫生睇吖嘛？<br />\n唯有靠勇武行動先有可能爭取到封關</span></strong>，正如爭取撤回送中條例一樣。"},{"pid":"b4b00482752eb898a6152ecac36e97b5aa136e28","tid":1855624,"uid":165136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T08:16:45.000Z","msg":"其實唔關中國人香港人外國人事<br />\n依家中國明顯係高危地區，武漢啲人一早逃走去到中國任何地區林鄭都唔係唔知<br />\n話唔全面封鎖中國嘅，咁攞證據證明嗰個城市無去過武漢嘅人進入先<br />\n林鄭見到中國官都奶鞋底咁，問人攞嘢一定攞唔到啦<br />\n所有由中國嚟香港嘅都要截<br />\n中國護照，香港身份證，外國passport都好<br />\n唔會因為個國藉而唔會感染，去過高危地區就有機會感染<br />\n最多係有香港身份證可以入境，但直接去隔離營<br />\n呢排仲要堅持去中國嘅就自己預定要返香港要去隔離營"},{"pid":"27063111a17d6af70e94bfa24e6f582ed5e65f45","tid":1855624,"uid":213747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3424a717cf348bac6bcb0a595acee2e68e21a31d","tid":1855624,"uid":62935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71fbddad9c0c15f6a4b4d11bef47b21fbc639572","tid":1855624,"uid":184370,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T07:43:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />洗乜做假，你都識講高官"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T07:44:56.000Z","msg":"權貴......親屬......"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T08:21:47.000Z","msg":"中共啲人叫港共整幾本passport俾佢全家有幾難"},{"pid":"995256401a0ac243e86c502d9e21a5aa374bda1b","tid":1855624,"uid":292644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T12:18:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好撚多人香港開工番大陸住.日日來回<br />\n不如借呢次cut走埋呢班假香港人</span>"},{"pid":"c4a290de36f52293093a491216448e0218f812e4","tid":1855624,"uid":62935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T12:37:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}